payload.message:
Drop the label into a flex container alongside the heading. For instance:

```tsx
import { Flex, Heading, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export function SectionHeader() {
  return (
    <Flex align="baseline" gap={2}>
      <Heading size="md">Payment Details</Heading>
      <Text fontSize="sm" color="gray.500">
        Optional
      </Text>
    </Flex>
  );
}
```

- `Flex` (or `HStack`) lines things up horizontally.
- `align="baseline"` keeps the bottoms of the text aligned.
- `Text` with `color="gray.500"` gives the subtle label; tweak the shade or fontSize as needed.

